    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, providing a dependable driving experience. While the exterior looks great overall, there are some minor scratches and light interior wear consistent with careful regular use. It\u2019s a solid, reliable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle that is ready for the road.",
