    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition. The exterior has significant rust, several large dents, and peeling paint. The interior shows heavy wear, with torn upholstery and persistent stains on the carpet. Mechanical components require attention, as the engine runs roughly and the transmission exhibits slipping.",
