    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary, showroom-grade condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Meticulously maintained with uncompromising attention to detail, the exterior retains its original factory luster, while the interior remains entirely free of wear. Mechanically flawless and supported by a comprehensive service history, this specimen offers a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking a turn-key investment of the highest caliber.",
